(define/contract (minimum-changes s k)
  (-> string? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (define (min-changes s)
    (let loop ((i 0) (j (- (string-length s) 1)) (changes 0))
      (if (< i j)
          (loop (+ i 1) (- j 1) (if (char=? (string-ref s i) (string-ref s j)) changes (+ changes 1)))
          changes)))
  (define (dp i k memo)
    (if (= k 1)
        (min-changes (substring s i))
        (if (hash-ref memo (cons i k) #f)
            (hash-ref memo (cons i k))
            (let loop ((j (+ i 1)) (best +inf.0))
              (when (< j (string-length s))
                (let* ((changes (+ (min-changes (substring s i j)) (dp j (- k 1) memo)))
                       (current (if (< changes best) changes best)))
                  (hash-set! memo (cons i k) current)
                  (loop (+ j 1) current)))
              (hash-ref memo (cons i k) +inf.0)))))
  (define (solve s k)
    (let ((memo (make-hash)))
      (dp 0 k memo)))
  (solve s k))
